t.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://www.stuff.co.nz/world/south-pacific/88661769/powerful-quake-hits-solomon-islands\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stuff.co.nz%2Fworld%2Fsouth-pacific%2F88661769%2Fpowerful-quake-hits-solomon-islands&d=BG%2Fn3Espi%2Fc13oue912U6UsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=cc0d8c0f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.stuff.co.nz/world/south-pacific/88661769/powerful-quake-hits-solomon-islands</a></span>"},{"pid":"a5b251cdf50ab4bffacee64ceb307b8669a038f2","tid":88710,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:03:56.000Z","msg":"M 8.0 - 40km W of Panguna, Papua New Guinea<br />\n<br />\n2017-01-22 04:30:24 UTC6.267&deg;S &nbsp; 155.119&deg;E153.8 km depth<br />\n<br />\nHAZARDOUS TSUNAMI WAVES FROM THIS EARTHQUAKE ARE POSSIBLE WITHIN THE NEXT THREE HOURS ALONG SOME COASTS OF PAPUA NEW GUINEA... SOLOMON ISLANDS... NAURU... POHNPEI... KOSRAE... VANUATU... CHUUK AND INDONESIA<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/njgm2orp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnjgm2orp&h=6d1e68b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42b7c89722b6c5127489355b0474283ac91f6db1","tid":88710,"uid":69680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:02:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/356004/xlarge/67292b7ff31454109f304449ac8de968.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F356004%2Fxlarge%2F67292b7ff31454109f304449ac8de968.jpg&h=ddbdaa9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/355258/xlarge/887aa69425fba7923bcddec3018685d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F355258%2Fxlarge%2F887aa69425fba7923bcddec3018685d2.jpg&h=444f4f10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅色火災危險警告下都幾難熄，呢場火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquot